div.div: Emergent diet composition of sprat, cod, and seals from the whole of the Baltic Sea.
div.p: Results are average from last 5 years of model 60-year calibration run for both juvenile and adult groups, with the prey being arranged on the x-axis according to the trophic level (A, C, E) and the dynamics of the diet composition simulated over the 60 yearsâ€“combined for adults and juveniles (B, D, F).
